-Ladies, here we are

00:00:02.535 --> 00:00:04.170 line:5%,start
in Los Angeles, California,

00:00:04.237 --> 00:00:05.605 line:5%,start
the city of dreams.

00:00:05.672 --> 00:00:07.774 line:5%,start
Laquifa, the postmodern pimp.

00:00:07.841 --> 00:00:09.642 line:5%,start
-Hi, everybody.
-What are you doing here?

00:00:09.709 --> 00:00:11.311 line:5%,start
I have kids that are working, too.

00:00:11.378 --> 00:00:12.679 line:5%,start
-Doing what? What show?
-I have--

00:00:12.746 --> 00:00:13.680 line:5%,start
Tell me what Broadway show she's in.

00:00:13.747 --> 00:00:14.748 line:5%,start
Well, she's not in a Broadway show.

00:00:14.814 --> 00:00:15.648 line:5%,start
Failure.

00:00:15.715 --> 00:00:18.184 line:5%,start
<i>You wanted an outside choreographer.</i>

00:00:18.251 --> 00:00:19.119 line:5%,start
Don't cry.

00:00:19.185 --> 00:00:20.120 line:5%,start
I'm not.

00:00:20.186 --> 00:00:22.188 line:5%,start
