00:00:22.255 --> 00:00:23.623 line:5%,start
<i>Right in the middle of the rehearsal,</i>

00:00:23.690 --> 00:00:25.125 line:5%,start
<i>I get a phone call from my mom.</i>

00:00:25.191 --> 00:00:28.128 line:5%,start
