00:00:29.662 --> 00:00:31.097 line:5%,start
<i>Coming up on </i>Dance Moms...

00:00:31.164 --> 00:00:32.966 line:5%,start
All right. Nationals in Tahoe.

00:00:33.033 --> 00:00:35.068 line:5%,start
We need to win.

00:00:35.135 --> 00:00:37.971 line:5%,start
Chloe tells me that she doesn't
want to dance anymore.

00:00:38.038 --> 00:00:40.540 line:5%,start
I have a whole list of people
that want to take her spot.

00:00:41.341 --> 00:00:44.511 line:5%,start
I really don't appreciate my ex-husband
checking up on me.

00:00:44.577 --> 00:00:46.479 line:5%,start
Take the crown and shove it up your ass.

00:00:47.480 --> 00:00:50.050 line:5%,start
I really need to get
these ladies in control

00:00:50.717 --> 00:00:53.119 line:5%,start
<i>before we step foot on a stage.</i>

00:00:53.186 --> 00:00:54.587 line:5%,start
Don't cry.

00:00:55.355 --> 00:00:57.390 line:5%,start
Your top Junior group.

